	<a  target="_blank" href="https://www.dlsite.com/maniax/dlaf/=/t/i/link/work/aid/momonoyu/id/RJ297540.html" rel="noopener sponsored"><img  class="target_type" border="0" src="//img.dlsite.jp/modpub/images2/work/doujin/RJ298000/RJ297540_img_main.jpg" itemprop="image"></a>
<br />
<br />サークル「Little Oasis」さんの同人音声作品。
<br />
